      "author_association" : "NONE",
      "body" : "Had the same issue on 16.10. \r\nI fixed the issue by installing libdb4.8-dev, by default even on 16.10 you get libdb5.3-dev and when you configure with --with-incompatible-bdb you get a segmentation fault.\r\n\r\nOn 17.10 which you say you're running you don't have 4.8 \r\nhttps://packages.ubuntu.com/artful/libdb++-dev\r\n\r\nYou might want to try bitcoin/contrib/install_db4.sh\r\n\r\n",
